---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Healthcare Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">

<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-400">
Healthcare Cybersecurity Solutions
</h1>

<p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
Healthcare organizations must protect patient data, medical devices,
and hospital infrastructure from cyber threats while maintaining compliance.
</p>

</section>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8 text-center">
Key Security Requirements for Healthcare
</h2>

<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Data Loss Prevention
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Protect sensitive patient data, electronic health records, and medical research.
</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
Recommended OEM: Forcepoint
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Endpoint Detection & Response
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Protect hospital endpoints, clinical systems, and medical workstations.
</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
Recommended OEM: SentinelOne / Trellix
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Vulnerability Management
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Identify and fix vulnerabilities across hospital IT infrastructure and medical devices.
</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
Recommended OEM: Tenable
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Privileged Access Management
</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Secure access to critical healthcare systems and administrative accounts.
</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
Recommended OEM: ARCON
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8 text-center">
Recommended OEM Vendors
</h2>

<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Forcepoint</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Protect sensitive healthcare data using Data Loss Prevention solutions.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">SentinelOne</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
AI-powered endpoint protection for hospital systems and clinical endpoints.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Trellix</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Advanced threat detection and endpoint protection for healthcare infrastructure.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Tenable</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Vulnerability management platform for healthcare IT infrastructure.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">ARCON</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
Privileged Access Management solution for securing healthcare administrative systems.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>